owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params.actualUserOpFeePerGas: The gas price this UserOp pays (unused)

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setAPNTsToken(address).details: Only owner can update. This is the token operators deposit to SuperPaymaster

setMinAPNTsBalance(uint256).details: Only owner can adjust this parameter

setMinOperatorStake(uint256).details: Only owner can adjust this parameter

params.newStake: New minimum stake amount in stGToken

setSuperPaymasterTreasury(address).details: Only owner can update. All operator deposits go to this address

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdrawTreasury(uint256).details: Only treasury can withdraw. This allows batch withdrawal to save gas

aPNTsPriceUSD().notice: aPNTs price in USD (18 decimals), e.g., 0.02 USD = 0.02e18

aPNTsToken().notice: aPNTs token address (AAStar community ERC20 token)

depositAPNTs(uint256).notice: Deposit aPNTs (Operator transfers aPNTs to SuperPaymaster contract)

executeSlashWithBLS(address,uint8,bytes).notice: Execute slash with BLS proof (only DVT Aggregator)

gasToUSDRate().notice: Gas to USD conversion rate (18 decimals), e.g., 4500e18 = $4500/ETH

isEligibleForUpgrade(address).notice: Check if operator is eligible for reputation upgrade

serviceFeeRate().notice: Service fee rate in basis points (200 = 2%)
